      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a new Outbound Route Filter (ORF) type, called the Covering Prefixes ORF (CP-ORF).  CP-ORF is applicable in Virtual Hub-and-Spoke VPNs.  It also is applicable in BGP/MPLS Ethernet VPN (EVPN) networks.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
